mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Created: create()
    Created --> Modified: modify()
    Modified --> Modified: modify()
    Created --> Deleted: delete()
    Modified --> Deleted: delete()
    
    state Created {
        [*] --> Validated: invariant_check
        Validated --> [*]
    }
    
    state Modified {
        [*] --> BusinessRuleCheck
        BusinessRuleCheck --> Applied: rule_passed
        BusinessRuleCheck --> Rejected: rule_failed
        Applied --> [*]
    }
    
    note right of Created
        聚合创建时:
        - 执行不变性校验
        - 发布 Created 事件
    end note
    
    note right of Modified
        状态变更时:
        - 封装业务规则在领域方法
        - 避免贫血模型
    end note
    
    classDef root fill:#e1f5fe,stroke:#01579b
    class Created,Modified,Deleted root